name: WorkKafe
overview:
WorkKafe is a gap-filler between “high on cost factor” big IT firms and “low on trust factor” freelancers.

WorkKafe is an IT solution provider that realizes the talent of highly competent enterprising software professionals, providing top quality IT solutions to progressive organizations and individuals.

WorkKafe’s mission is to reinvent freelancing as the better choice for superior solutions rather than low cost solutions, by providing individuals freedom of time and space, allowing them blend creativity with intellect working with an open mind, and letting companies gain from indulgence of free spirited talent.

WorkKafe aspires to celebrate the spirit of entrepreneurship by providing competent opportunities to enterprising professionals and high quality services to progressive organizations.
